text: Alfredo Fernández Durán (born 2 February 1964) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Madrid
